JOHNSON v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 33,

September Term, 1960.]

Decided November 17, 1960.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

Per Curiam:.

The application for leave to appeal is denied for the reasons set forth in the opinion of the trial court.
